in-w-0 [overflow-wrap:anywhere] whitespace-pre-wrap">eski footerdaki  premium havayı istiyorum</div></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div aria-label="Mesajınızın işlemleri" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="İletiyi kopyala" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-1a29ccf4.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="İletiyi düzenle" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-1a29ccf4.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section></div><div class="" data-turn-id-container="3057770e-a2bf-4522-b6a8-bb18f615c404" data-is-intersecting="true"><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto R6Vx5W_threadScrollVars scroll-mb-[calc(var(--scroll-root-safe-area-inset-bottom,0px)+var(--thread-response-height))] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="3057770e-a2bf-4522-b6a8-bb18f615c404" data-turn-id-container="3057770e-a2bf-4522-b6a8-bb18f615c404" data-testid="conversation-turn-18" data-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div data-conversation-screenshot-content="" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="becafb8b-12d2-4673-aa75-9cef53c142f6" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="183">Aynen abim, istediğin şey şu: <strong data-start="30" data-end="93">eski footer’ın o premium/lacivert-gold vitrin havası kalsın</strong>, ama eski footer’daki gibi içerikler üst üste binmesin ve her sayfada farklı davranmasın.</p>
<p data-start="185" data-end="381" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Ben şimdi şu mantığa döndürüyorum:<br data-start="219" data-end="222">
<strong data-start="222" data-end="266">tek tip footer + eski premium görsel dil</strong>. Yani eski tasarımın ruhunu alacağız, kırılgan absolute yerleşimi bırakacağız. Logo kırılması da ayrıca çözülecek.</p></div></div></div><span class="group/tool-message"><span class="block first:mt-0 relative text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary my-1.5"><div class="group start-0 top-0 me-1.5 overflow-hidden mt-1 text-start"><button class="inline-block" style="opacity: 1;"><div class="flex items-center justify-start gap-1"><span class="text-start">Uygulama yanıtı alındı</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-1a29ccf4.svg#ba3792" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></div></span></span><div class="mt-1 flex flex-wrap gap-2 empty:hidden"></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="3719ace9-e757-4892-a4ee-9ca2998b9a73" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="319" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Tamam abim, eski premium havayı geri taşıyorum ama “eski kırılgan footer” olarak değil. Şu anki <code data-start="96" data-end="112">footer-unified</code> yapısının içine eski footer’daki <strong data-start="146" data-end="208">cam panel, gold çizgi, dalga zemin, büyük logo/marka alanı</strong> hissini koyacağım. Logo için de kırılma ihtimalini bitirmek adına çalışan <code data-start="283" data-end="305">header-logo-only.png</code> kullanacağım.</p></div></div></div><span class="group/tool-message"><span class="block first:mt-0 relative text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary my-1.5"><div class="group start-0 top-0 me-1.5 overflow-hidden mt-1 text-start"><button class="inline-block" style="opacity: 1;"><div class="flex items-center justify-start gap-1"><span class="text-start">Uygulama yanıtı alındı</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-1a29ccf4.svg#ba3792" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></div></span></span><div class="mt-1 flex flex-wrap gap-2 empty:hidden"></div><span class="group/tool-message"><span class="block first:mt-0 relative text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary my-1.5"><div class="group start-0 top-0 me-1.5 overflow-hidden mt-1 text-start"><button class="inline-block" style="opacity: 1;"><div class="flex items-center justify-start gap-1"><span class="text-start">Uygulama yanıtı alındı</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-1a29ccf4.svg#ba3792" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></div></span></span><div class="mt-1 flex flex-wrap gap-2 empty:hidden"></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="9adc9aab-c5c0-493f-a89b-5e1b9c31f731" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="174" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Şimdi kontrol ediyorum abim: yeni footer’ın eski premium görseli kullandığı, kırık <code data-start="83" data-end="100">footer-logo.png</code> referansının kalktığı ve mobilde fallback logo olduğu doğru mu bakıyorum.</p></div></div></div><span class="group/tool-message"><span class="block first:mt-0 relative text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary my-1.5"><div class="group start-0 top-0 me-1.5 overflow-hidden mt-1 text-start"><button class="inline-block" style="opacity: 1;"><div class="flex items-center justify-start gap-1"><span class="text-start">Uygulama yanıtı alındı</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-1a29ccf4.svg#ba3792" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></div></span></span><div class="mt-1 flex flex-wrap gap-2 empty:hidden"></div><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div class="flex min-w-0 items-center"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-tertiary hover:text-token-text-primary dark:hover:text-token-text-primary flex items-center gap-0.5 text-start dark:text-(--interactive-label-tertiary-default)">2m 55s boyunca düşündüm<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="icon-xs"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-1a29ccf4.svg#b140e7" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="393b6d8d-71cd-4442-882c-c3a83e1321a0" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="226">Haklısın abim, “eski footer premiumluğu” dediğin şey aslında o <strong data-start="63" data-end="128">lacivert/gold özel görsel zemin + cam panel + dalga detayları</strong>. Yeni sade footer onu öldürmüştü. Şimdi onu geri taşıdım ama eski hatalı yapıya dönmeden yaptım ✅</p>
<p data-start="228" data-end="241">Yaptığım şey:</p>
<ul data-start="243" data-end="883">
<li data-section-id="2w8wmf" data-start="243" data-end="336">
<p data-start="245" data-end="336">Footer hâlâ <strong data-start="257" data-end="283">tek tip unified footer</strong> olarak çalışıyor; yani tüm sayfalarda aynı sistem.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1o3c6mp" data-start="337" data-end="440">
<p data-start="339" data-end="440">Eski premium görsel zemin tekrar kullanılıyor: <code data-start="386" data-end="415">footer-background-clean.png</code> arka plana geri alındı.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="phkna6" data-start="441" data-end="583">
<p data-start="443" data-end="583">Sol taraftaki eski Dumanlar / Bitke / Mofiy premium marka alanı için desktopta zemin görseli kullanılıyor; üstüne kırık logo bindirmiyorum.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12asjqu" data-start="584" data-end="693">
<p data-start="586" data-end="693">Sayfalar, üretim alanları ve iletişim yine gerçek HTML link olarak kaldı; yani tıklanabilir ve responsive.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="bwbdkf" data-start="694" data-end="811">
<p data-start="696" data-end="811">Tablet/mobilde eski görsel zemin bozulmasın diye ayrıca <code data-start="752" data-end="774">header-logo-only.png</code> ile temiz fallback marka alanı var.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="156qr3d" data-start="812" data-end="883">
<p data-start="814" data-end="883">Kırık <code data-start="820" data-end="837">footer-logo.png</code> referansı kaldırıldı; artık o hata olmayacak.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="885" data-end="902">Commit: <code data-start="893" data-end="902">748f17d</code></p>
<p data-start="904" data-end="1003" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Canlıda <code data-start="912" data-end="923">Ctrl + F5</code> yapınca eski premium havaya yakın ama daha stabil bir footer görmen lazım abim.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="relative h-[60px] select-none"><div class="absolute h-[60px]" style="opacity: 1;"><button class="not-prose group/footnote border-token-border-default bg-token-main-surface-primary hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 mt-3 mb-2 flex w-fit items-center gap-1.5 rounded-xl border py-2 ps-3 pe-2.5"><div class="flex flex-row-reverse gap-1"><div class="border-token-main-surface-primary bg-token-main-surface-primary flex items-center overflow-hidden group-hover/footnote:border-token-main-surface-secondary relative" style="opacity: 1;"><div class="icon-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-external-a2895b13.svg#1a6f23" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></div></div><div class="text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-0.5 text-xs font-semibold">Kaynaklar</div></button></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Yanıt işlemleri" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" st