.</span><span>text((</span><span class="ͼj">1302</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">cy</span><span class="ͼg">+</span><span class="ͼj">20</span><span class="ͼg">+</span><span class="ͼm">j</span><span class="ͼg">*</span><span class="ͼj">20</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼm">line</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">font</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼm">f_small_b</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">fill</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼm">white</span><span>)</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼm">draw</span><span class="ͼg">.</span><span>line((</span><span class="ͼj">1302</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">cy</span><span class="ͼg">+</span><span class="ͼj">58</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼj">1638</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">cy</span><span class="ͼg">+</span><span class="ͼj">58</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼm">fill</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼj">255</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼj">255</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼj">255</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼj">38</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼm">width</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼj">1</span><span>)</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼm">cy</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">+=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼj">78</span><br><br><span class="ͼe"># Social icons</span><br><span class="ͼm">sx</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">sy</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼj">1240</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼj">482</span><br><span class="ͼg">for</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">i</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">label</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">in</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">enumerate</span><span>([</span><span class="ͼk">"in"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼk">"ig"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼk">"yt"</span><span>]):</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼm">cx</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">sx</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">+</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">i</span><span class="ͼg">*</span><span class="ͼj">62</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼm">draw</span><span class="ͼg">.</span><span>ellipse((</span><span class="ͼm">cx</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">sy</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">cx</span><span class="ͼg">+</span><span class="ͼj">48</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">sy</span><span class="ͼg">+</span><span class="ͼj">48</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼm">outline</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼm">gold2</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">width</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼj">2</span><span>)</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼm">draw</span><span class="ͼg">.</span><span>text((</span><span class="ͼm">cx</span><span class="ͼg">+</span><span class="ͼj">12</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">sy</span><span class="ͼg">+</span><span class="ͼj">13</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼm">label</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">font</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼm">font</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼj">17</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼj">True</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼm">fill</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼm">gold</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼe"># Center emblem and bottom</span><br><span class="ͼm">center_x</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">W</span><span class="ͼg">//</span><span class="ͼj">2</span><br><span class="ͼm">draw</span><span class="ͼg">.</span><span>ellipse((</span><span class="ͼm">center_x</span><span class="ͼg">-</span><span class="ͼj">39</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">H</span><span class="ͼg">-</span><span class="ͼj">128</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">center_x</span><span class="ͼg">+</span><span class="ͼj">39</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">H</span><span class="ͼg">-</span><span class="ͼj">50</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼm">fill</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼj">4</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼj">17</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼj">31</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼm">outline</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼm">gold2</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">width</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼj">2</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼm">draw</span><span class="ͼg">.</span><span>text((</span><span class="ͼm">center_x</span><span class="ͼg">-</span><span class="ͼj">18</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">H</span><span class="ͼg">-</span><span class="ͼj">125</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼk">"D"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">font</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼm">f_emblem</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">fill</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼm">gold</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼm">draw</span><span class="ͼg">.</span><span>text((</span><span class="ͼj">130</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">H</span><span class="ͼg">-</span><span class="ͼj">56</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼk">"© 2026 Dumanlar A.S. Tum haklari saklidir."</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">font</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼm">f_tiny</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">fill</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼm">soft</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼm">legal</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼk">"KVKK Aydinlatma Metni     |     Gizlilik Politikasi     |     Cerez Politikasi"</span><br><span class="ͼm">bbox</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">draw</span><span class="ͼg">.</span><span>textbbox((</span><span class="ͼj">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼj">0</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼm">legal</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">font</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼm">f_tiny</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼm">draw</span><span class="ͼg">.</span><span>text((</span><span class="ͼm">W</span><span class="ͼg">-</span><span class="ͼj">130</span><span class="ͼg">-</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼm">bbox</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼj">2</span><span>]</span><span class="ͼg">-</span><span class="ͼm">bbox</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼj">0</span><span>]), </span><span class="ͼm">H</span><span class="ͼg">-</span><span class="ͼj">56</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼm">legal</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">font</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼm">f_tiny</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">fill</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼm">soft</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼm">draw</span><span class="ͼg">.</span><span>text((</span><span class="ͼj">70</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼj">24</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼk">"Premium Footer Mockup / Desktop gorunum"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">font</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼm">font</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼj">18</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼj">True</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼm">fill</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼj">205</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼj">210</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼj">218</span><span>))</span><br><br><span class="ͼm">out</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">Path</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼk">"/mnt/data/dumanlar_premium_footer_mockup.png"</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼm">img</span><span class="ͼg">.</span><span>convert(</span><span class="ͼk">"RGB"</span><span>)</span><span class="ͼg">.</span><span>save(</span><span class="ͼm">out</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">quality</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼj">95</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼm">print</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼm">out</span><span class="ͼg">.</span><span>as_posix())</span><br></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div><div class="bg-token-bg-secondary-surface overflow-x-auto p-4 text-xs corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="mb-1 text-gray-400">STDOUT/STDERR</div><div class="prose flex flex-col-reverse text-black"><pre class="shrink-0 overflow-auto"><span class="">/mnt/data/dumanlar_premium_footer_mockup.png
</span></pre></div></div></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="decee72b-f257-4797-9091-71223c4f1982" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="100">Aynen abim, en doğru hamle bu oldu. Önce görsel tasarımı netleştirelim, sonra kodu ona göre yaparız.</p>
<p data-start="102" data-end="147">Şöyle bir <strong data-start="112" data-end="137">premium footer mockup</strong> çıkardım:</p>
<p data-start="149" data-end="240"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" type="button">Footer tasarım görselini indir / aç</button></span></p>
<p data-start="242" data-end="525">Bu tasarımda eski footer’daki premium hava korunuyor: lacivert-gold zemin, cam panel, sol büyük marka alanı, ortada sayfalar/ürün grupları, sağda temiz iletişim bloğu ve altta yasal linkler. Ama eski footer’daki gibi üst üste binme riski olmayacak şekilde grid mantığında düşünülmüş.</p>
