se></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="İletiyi düzenle" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-1a29ccf4.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section></div><div class="" data-turn-id-container="request-6a364c95-8390-83eb-9e4e-50784ec9b908-7" data-is-intersecting="true" style="--last-known-height: 72px;"><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto R6Vx5W_threadScrollVars scroll-mb-[calc(var(--scroll-root-safe-area-inset-bottom,0px)+var(--thread-response-height))] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="request-6a364c95-8390-83eb-9e4e-50784ec9b908-7" data-turn-id-container="request-6a364c95-8390-83eb-9e4e-50784ec9b908-7" data-testid="conversation-turn-22" data-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div data-conversation-screenshot-content="" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div class="flex min-w-0 items-center"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-tertiary hover:text-token-text-primary dark:hover:text-token-text-primary flex items-center gap-0.5 text-start dark:text-(--interactive-label-tertiary-default)">16s boyunca düşündüm<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="icon-xs"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-1a29ccf4.svg#b140e7" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="5cdbb242-f585-460c-abfd-8ec1a8ee815a" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="294">Abim tam böyle görünmesi için <strong data-start="30" data-end="107">şu anki footer’ı yamayarak değil, baştan bu tasarıma göre kurmamız lazım.</strong> Çünkü bu görseldeki şey “tek parça premium footer kompozisyonu”; mevcut sitedeki footer ise farklı sayfalarda farklı HTML + üstüne runtime CSS ile ittirilen bir yapı. O yüzden bozuluyor.</p>
<p data-start="296" data-end="312">En doğru yol şu:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="10kafly" data-start="314" data-end="350">1. Footer’ı tek kaynak yapacağız</h3>
<p data-start="352" data-end="519">Tüm sayfalarda farklı footer HTML’i varsa onları dikkate almayacağız. Sayfa açılınca <code data-start="437" data-end="446">main.js</code> içinden değilse bile tercihen <strong data-start="477" data-end="508">tek bir ortak footer yapısı</strong> basılacak.</p>
<p data-start="521" data-end="532">Yani hedef:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="534" data-end="593"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-1a29ccf4.svg#fa6359" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>HTML</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><div role="group" aria-label="Kod bloku görünümü" class="group/code-block-preview-toggle relative flex items-center gap-0.5"><div aria-hidden="true" class="pointer-events-none absolute start-0 top-0 size-9 rounded-full bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/10 motion-safe:transition-transform motion-safe:duration-200 motion-safe:ease-in-out translate-x-0 group-has-[[data-code-block-preview-toggle-preview]:hover]/code-block-preview-toggle:translate-x-[calc(100%+2px)] group-has-[[data-code-block-preview-toggle-preview]:focus-visible]/code-block-preview-toggle:translate-x-[calc(100%+2px)]"></div><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Kod" aria-pressed="true" class="relative z-1 flex size-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full motion-safe:transition-colors text-token-text-primary" data-code-block-preview-toggle-code="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-1a29ccf4.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Önizleme" aria-pressed="false" aria-disabled="false" class="relative z-1 flex size-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full motion-safe:transition-colors text-token-text-primary" data-code-block-preview-toggle-preview="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-1a29ccf4.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Kopyala" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-1a29ccf4.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative" data-custom-highlighting-behavior="boundary"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative [container-type:inline-size]"><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto" style="transform: none; max-height: 56.25cqw;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼo">&lt;footer</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">class</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"premium-footer"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;</span><br><span>  ...</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;/footer&gt;</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="595" data-end="620">Tüm sayfalarda aynı yapı.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="tvnu25" data-start="622" data-end="702">2. Bu görseli “arka plan resmi” gibi değil, gerçek HTML/CSS olarak kuracağız</h3>
<p data-start="704" data-end="731">Şu görselde 4 ana alan var:</p>
<ul data-start="733" data-end="886">
<li data-section-id="1bg89rg" data-start="733" data-end="798">
<p data-start="735" data-end="798">Sol marka alanı: Dumanlar logo + Bitke / Mofiy + değer ikonları</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1qf1rmj" data-start="799" data-end="809">
<p data-start="801" data-end="809">Sayfalar</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="235sfz" data-start="810" data-end="827">
<p data-start="812" data-end="827">Üretim Alanları</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="3z5son" data-start="828" data-end="838">
<p data-start="830" data-end="838">İletişim</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="mag01i" data-start="839" data-end="886">
<p data-start="841" data-end="886">Alt telif / KVKK çizgisi / ortadaki D amblemi</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="888" data-end="985">Bunların hepsi ayrı ayrı HTML olacak. Böylece linkler tıklanabilir kalır, mobilde düzgün kırılır.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="hgiz6c" data-start="987" data-end="1046">3. Eski premium havayı veren efektler CSS ile yapılacak</h3>
<p data-start="1048" data-end="1071">Şunları CSS’e alacağız:</p>
<ul data-start="1073" data-end="1306">
<li data-section-id="1cp8dfo" data-start="1073" data-end="1101">
<p data-start="1075" data-end="1101">Lacivert degrade arka plan</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="4xt4eh" data-start="1102" data-end="1118">
<p data-start="1104" data-end="1118">Gold üst çizgi</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="pkulin" data-start="1119" data-end="1141">
<p data-start="1121" data-end="1141">Cam panel / iç gölge</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fndhdl" data-start="1142" data-end="1176">
<p data-start="1144" data-end="1176">Kolon ayırıcı ince gold çizgiler</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="fxvi69" data-start="1177" data-end="1202">
<p data-start="1179" data-end="1202">Alttaki dalga çizgileri</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="eymtgv" data-start="1203" data-end="1232">
<p data-start="1205" data-end="1232">Ortadaki yuvarlak D amblemi</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1wkvnxt" data-start="1233" data-end="1267">
<p data-start="1235" data-end="1267">Sol logonun büyük premium duruşu</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1shsdgj" data-start="1268" data-end="1306">
<p data-start="1270" data-end="1306">İletişim ikonlarının gold çemberleri</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="19comae" data-start="1308" data-end="1350">4. Masaüstü ve mobil ayrı tasarlanacak</h3>
<p data-start="1352" data-end="1393">Desktopta bu görsel gibi 4 kolon duracak.</p>
<p data-start="1395" data-end="1420">Mobilde ise şöyle olmalı:</p>
<ol data-start="1422" data-end="1519">
<li data-section-id="1jlt6rl" data-start="1422" data-end="1443">
<p data-start="1425" data-end="1443">Logo / marka bloğu</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="la8wmi" data-start="1444" data-end="1455">
<p data-start="1447" data-end="1455">Sayfalar</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1xwk233" data-start="1456" data-end="1474">
<p data-start="1459" data-end="1474">Üretim Alanları</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1itgtfk" data-start="1475" data-end="1486">
<p data-start="1478" data-end="1486">İletişim</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="p6hykx" data-start="1487" data-end="1502">
<p data-start="1490" data-end="1502">Sosyal medya</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1bkuwsg" data-start="1503" data-end="1519">
<p data-start="1506" data-end="1519">Yasal linkler</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1521" data-end="1611">Yani mobilde bu görseli sıkıştırmayacağız; aynı premium dili koruyup dikey tasarlayacağız.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1sa896x" data-start="1613" data-end="1652">5. Şu anki karmaşayı temizleyeceğiz</h3>
<p data-start="1654" data-end="1674">En önemlisi bu abim:</p>
<ul data-start="1676" data-end="1872">
<li data-section-id="s2tjkb" data-start="1676" data-end="1692">
<p data-start="1678" data-end="1692"><code data-start="1678" data-end="1692">footer-exact</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1tqued8" data-start="1693" data-end="1711">
<p data-start="1695" data-end="1711"><code data-start="1695" data-end="1711">footer-unified</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1n4uz7e" data-start="1712" data-end="1739">
<p data-start="1714" data-end="1739">eski footer override’ları</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1rr5f2g" data-start="1740" data-end="1804">
<p data-start="1742" data-end="1804"><code data-start="1742" data-end="1761">bitke-refresh.css</code> içinde footer’a sonradan basan düzeltmeler</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="110usd9" data-start="1805" data-end="1872">
<p data-start="1807" data-end="1872"><code data-start="1807" data-end="1816">main.js</code> içinde footer’ı sürekli yeniden yazan karmaşık bölümler</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1874" data-end="1964">Bunları sadeleştirip tek sistem bırakacağız. Yoksa her yeni düzeltmede başka sayfa patlar.</p>
<p data-start="1966" data-end="2119" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Benim önerim net: <strong data-start="1984" data-end="2049">Bu görseli hedef alıp <code data-start="2008" data-end="2024">premium-footer</code> diye sıfırdan yapalım.</strong> Eski footer’daki premium ruhu koruruz ama altyapıyı tertemiz yaparız.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Yanıt işlemleri" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Yanıtı kopyala" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-1a29ccf4.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Paylaş" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-1a29ccf4.s